+/**
+ * GGUF Model Loader
+ *
+ * Parses GGUF model files and extracts weights for WebGPU inference.
+ * Supports any transformer-based text or image encoder.
+ *
+ * GGUF Format:
+ * - Magic: "GGUF" (4 bytes)
+ * - Version: u32
+ * - Tensor count: u64
+ * - Metadata KV count: u64
+ * - Metadata key-value pairs
+ * - Tensor info (name, dims, type, offset)
+ * - Tensor data (aligned)
